about.page_head.title: About Us | Closest Tow Truck | 24/7 Auto Rescue
about.page_head.desc: The information you are looking for about Chekici is on this page. You can have your vehicle transported in-city, inter-city and in singular or multiple way with Chekici. You can find out the prices of auto tow trucks. On this page, you can eliminate the question marks that arise in your head about Chekici.

about.container.title: Get to know Chekici Auto Tow Truck,
about.container.content_text_1: CHEKICI LOJİSTİK BİLİŞİM SANAYİ VE TİCARET LİMİTED ŞİRKETİ that has set out to the road as a joint venture of Izmir based 35inch Software Solutions and Kristy International Trade & Transportation, which provides services in all the leading countries of the world in the field of trade. Chekici, which is one of the fruits of this initiative that combines technological and innovative approaches with extensive trading experience from different sectors, offers a unique experience for its visitors by revealing its difference from the first moment it sets out. Whether you are a car dealer looking for frequent car transportation services, a user looking for roadside assistance due to an urgent need, or a person providing car transportation services... Chekici brings all the services you may need for inner-city and intercity car transportation to your fingertips in a quality and safe way!,

general.company_address: İNÖNÜ MAH. MUAMMER AKSOY CAD. NİVO İSTANBUL A BLOK NO: 125 İÇ KAPI NO: 101 KÜÇÜKÇEKMECE/ İSTANBUL
general.slider_supplier4_body:
By combining their powers, Chekici and Petrol Ofisi create an advantageous fuel opportunity for tow truck companies!
All towing companies registered to the PO application receive 4% discount on all fuel purchases they make from Petrol Ofisi!
general.slider_supplier1_body:
Requests are in your cell instantly!
Customers are able to create a request from location to location inside the Chekici application. When customers create a request, if they are within the city and district route where you work, they come to your phone as push notification. Thus, you can instantly view customer needs and reach your customers by sending offers quickly to the requests.
You have to send an offer within 5 minutes to the incoming request. Since there are different tow trucks that have a deal with Chekici in the same route, whether your offer wil be confirmed or not is up to do customer.
Hundreds of vehicle transfers take place every day within the Chekici application. Thanks to this large transaction volume, it is easier for towing companies to operate at full capacity and customers can quickly access the towing service they are always looking for.
It is very easy now to access wide customer portfolio of Chekici and to increase your income by partnering up with Chekici!
general.slider_supplier2_body:
Chekici is a platform created with the purpose of providing uninterrupted 24/7 towing service to you in all districts and cities of Turkey. There are thousands of towing companies in all cities and districts of Turkey that provide towing services within Chekici. It aims to provide uninterrupted service to its customers with Chekici app that has the widest, most reliable network.
If the request that the customer has created within your transfer route, you will get notification. You have to send an offer within 5 minutes to the incoming request. Since there are different tow trucks that have a deal with Chekici in the same route, whether your offer wil be confirmed or not is up to do customer.
Hundreds of vehicle transfers take place every day within the Chekici application. Thanks to this large transaction volume, it is easier for towing companies to operate at full capacity and customers can quickly access the towing service they are always looking for.
general.slider_supplier3_body:
Hundreds of vehicles are transported every day thanks to Chekici!
There is a wide customer pool and thousands of towing companies in every area of Turkey within Chekici. With the Chekici application, more than a hundred deals are made every day and they move on to the transport stage.
Thanks to this large transaction volume, it is easier for tow companies to work with full capacity and it is easier for customers to access to towing service that they are looking for 24/7
general.slider_supplier5_body:
A first in Vehicle Towing Service! Watch the Tow Truck Vehicle Live!
You also can meet with our tow truck live video service, which we started to serve with our pilot vehicles. It is time to manage your tranportation process whether they are in Chekici platform or other platforms!
Contact with us now to be able to track your tow trucks with live location support! Call our call center to enroll in our pre-request list!
general.slider_customer1_body:
Offers are in your cell within 5 minutes with Chekici!
Start and End locations of your request are forwarded to the tow trucks in the area that give service instantaneously. Your personal information is not shared with the tow trucks. As a result of your request, you will be presented a price offer from several tow trucks alternatively within 5 minutes.
As soon as the price offer is sent to you, this offer will be delivered to you through in-app notification, sms and e-mail. You can confirm the offer that suits to you with a single touch from the 'requests' tab inside our application.
general.slider_customer2_body:
Chekici provides towing service in every cities and districts of Turkey 24/7.
There are thousands of towing companies that give service in every cities and districts of Turkey within Chekici. With the Chekici application, which has the widest and most reliable vehicle transportation network, serving in 81 provinces, we come to your rescue instantly wherever you are!
Hundreds of vehicle transfers are made every day within the Chekici application from any location. Thanks to this large transaction volume, it is easier for towing companies to operate at full capacity and customers can quickly access the towing service they are always looking for.
general.slider_customer3_body:
Hundreds of vehicles are transported every day thanks to Chekici!
There are thousands of towing companies portfolio that provides service in every area of Turkey within Chekici. We rush to the aid of all vehicles that have malfunctions, broken, out of battery, out of fuel or even newly bought or to be delivered to their new owner. We are at your service with our fully equipped team and our high-end equipments. We are in the field with our vehicles that can tow any type vehicle. Thus, as Chekici road assistance firm; we can rescue any type of vehicle such as minibus, truck, pick-up etc.
With the Chekici application, more than a hundred deals are made every day and they move on to the transport stage. Thanks to this large transaction volume, it is easier for towing companies to operate at full capacity and customers can quickly access the towing service they are always looking for.
general.slider_customer5_body:
Turkey's express towing service with the most routes is at Chekici!
We can transfer your car directly in Istanbul-Izmir, Istanbul-Ankara, Istanbul-Antalya, Istanbul-Sanliurfa, Istanbul-Diyarbakir, Ankara-Konya, Istanbul-Konya and many more regions, depending on availability, on any day and at any time. Chekici express service operates on certain city routes in order to provide direct and fast vehicle transfer.
general.slider_customer4_body:
Keep your vehicles safe with 'Towing Liability Insurance'.
Towing liability insurance is a transportation insurance in which legal liabilities arising as a result of the realization of a risk during the transportation of your vehicles are covered within the conditions and limits specified in the policy. All towing vehicles within the Chekici application have 'Towing liability insurance'.
If the customer requests it before the transfer process, the tow truck must create a 'Carrier liability policy'. In this way, the damage that may occur during the transportation of the vehicle is covered by the liability insurance of the tow truck carrying the vehicle. Do not forget to request a 'Carrier liability policy' before the transfer process.
The legal process that will take place in case of damage and loss takes place between you and the towing company. Chekici is definitely not a party.
general.slider_customer6_body:
Parking lot service is at Chekici!
With Chekici, we can easily pick up your car from the location you specify, keep it in Chekici contracted car parks in 81 provinces of Turkey, and transfer it to the location you specify on the date you wish. For detailed information about our contracted parking tariffs, you can call our customer support line at 0(544) 535 50 04.
general.slider_customer7_body:
Towing companies within Chekici, can upload their insurance, tax board to the system. When you look at the company profile, you can see whether a company that has submitted an offer to your request has these documents, and you can choose the company that creates a more reliable impression.
Since this system makes the towing companies that uploaded this documents more reliable than other towing companies that did not upload, it creates a safer ecosystem for all of our users. Our towing company serves its customers safely and within the scope of the invoice. In short, all of our vehicles are fully insured against any setbacks. Thus, your vehicles are secured in cases such as possible rollovers and accidents.
general.slider_customer8_body:
A first in Vehicle Towing service!
It is time for you to now watch the Tow Truck vehicle live with the updates that we have brought to our system. Your vehicle transportation process will now happen in front of your eyes!
You can easily track when will your vehicle hit the road, where it is and when will it delivered with the camera live location support through our mobile application. By adding a new towing solution to the alternative towing solutions, we are giving you a peace of mind.
By creating your tow truck request immediately, you can also meet with our tow truck live video service, which we started to serve with our pilot vehicles.
